            <div type="transcript" id="F327A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How the old Mountains drip<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 with Sunset</l>
                    <l>How the Hemlocks burn - </l>
                    <l>How the Dun Brake is draped<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 in Cinder </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="By the Wizard Sun -">By the Setting Sun -</add>
By the Wizard Sun -</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How the old Steeples hand<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 the Scarlet</l>
                    <l>Till the Ball is full - </l>
                    <l>Have I the lip of the Flamingo </l>
                    <l>That I dare to tell?  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then, how the Fire ebbs like Billows - </l>
                    <l>Touching all the Grass</l>
                    <l>With a departing - Sapphire - feature - </l>
                    <l>As a Duchess passed - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How a small Dusk crawls<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 on the Village </l>
                    <l>Till the Houses blot </l>
                    <l>And the odd Flambeau, no men<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 carry<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
</l>
                    <l>Glimmer on the Street - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How it is Night - in Nest<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 and Kennel - </l>
                    <l>And where was the Wood - </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Just a Dome of Abyss is Bowing">Acres of Masts are standing</add>
Just a Dome of Abyss is Bowing</l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Into Solitude">back of Solitude</add>
<add type="alternate" extent="Into">next to - &amp;#x2022; At the &amp;#x2022; After - &amp;#x2022; Unto</add>
Into Solitude -</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>These are the<add type="alternate" extent="Visions">Fashions -</add>
 Visions<add type="alternate" extent="flitted">baffled -</add>
 flitted<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Guido - </l>
                    <l>Titian - never told - </l>
                    <l>Domenichino dropped his pencil - </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Paralyzed, with Gold -">Powerless to unfold -</add>
Paralyzed, with Gold</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
